#ROOMS
#13500
Bottom-level stairway~
Walking down the creaking stairs, smells of perfumes, mixed in 
with cigarettes and mild liquor float about the air. All kinds 
of people are walking around, ranging from dark elves to espers. 
In this bar, all are welcome, as long as the place remains 
peaceful.
~
