#13501
Top of the stairwell~
Leading to the lower levels of the bar, the black stairway bends around 
the corner. On the walls are flyers for various bands and pictures of 
great heroes of Neo-Toyko. In the middle is a plaque that reads-
                    "Monument to those we have served"
                                 Signed,
                             The management.
~
