#13502
Near the stairs~
People are walking all around, shoving their way through the mobs 
of others. Sometimes there is an occasional trip-up and a fight 
breaks loose, but most of the time people here seem relaxed. The 
ceiling above you is a dark shade of black, and there are posters 
advertising for local Neo-Tokyo bands all around. The black-lights 
reflect off of them and it's hard not to stare off into their 
magnetic haze.
~
