#13503
A hazy smoke-filled room~
Around this bend, there are large tables, each with chairs around 
them. Further ahead are bar tables where you can order anything from 
a martini to a whiskey sour. Lining the bar tables are many ashtrays, 
filled with cigarette butts, and some even have spilled corn-nuts with 
burn marks on them. Large clouds of smoke fill this room, enough to 
make one choke, unless they're used to this kind of atmosphere.
~
