#13504
Near the snack-bar~
Smells of pretzels and other assorted goods inter-mingle with the 
hovering smoke that floods the nostrils of anyone entering this 
section of the bar. Seats line the walls and leave enough space 
for a small person to squeeze in line for something to eat here, 
while people walk around holding there drinks and trying to 
converse. The black lights from the sides of the room illuminate 
across faces and light up any bright clothing. Speakers line the 
walls and seem to blast straight into the face of any passerbys.
~
