#13505
A hazy smoke-filled room~
Walking through this bend, you come across a section of large tables,
each with a cluster of chairs surrounding them. Up ahead is a strip
of the bar where you can order anything from martinis to whiskey sours.
Along each seat you notice numerous ash-trays that have been filled 
with cigarette butts and other non-identified burn-marked stuff. The
other noticed effect is the enormous smoke cloud that hovers around
the lights, giving off a hazy impression as you pass by.
