#13506
Near the kitchen~
Wonderful scents emit from just around the corner, filling everyone's 
noses with good things. There are a few small seats here, enough to 
relax and hide away from the masses and relax with your drink. This 
places seems cleaner than the rest, maybe for health reasons, but it 
is sure enough a choice place to sit and chat with a few other friends.
