#13507
In the kitchen~
Large metal tables line the kitchen walls and hold many various items, 
either food or for food preperation. Near the back is a sink, used for 
the washing of hands before any food may be touched or serviced. Music 
can still be heard playing outside, as well as the idle chat and 
laughter that fill this bar.
