Upper-level stairway~
It's much less smoky up here, but definitely not quieter.  There is music 
simply oozing from every pore of every person in here.  The dance floor is 
full ofpeople doing all sorts of dancing. Also, the faint thunk of darts 
hitting a dartboard and the almost-musical click of one pool ball hitting
one another can be heard.
