#13514
Billards Room~
Dominated by a tournament size pool table, there is just enough room for 
a player to fully extend his or her cue stick to the wall.  The pool and 
darts area is the only part of the upper level of the bar where smoking 
is allowed.  Large vents in the ceiling keep the smoke from leaking into 
the dance floor.
