#13516
A lounge~
On the slightly pock-marked north wall are two sets of dartboards, each with 
its own matching set of darts.  A chalkboard hangs between them for keeping 
score, if one is concerned with the outcome of the game.  The east wall is 
plastered with postered advertising movies soon to be coming out in local 
theaters. The sounds of billiard balls clicking against one another drift 
from the south.
