#13517
A unisex bathroom~
As bar bathrooms go, this one is a good one.  The fixtures, while not 
gleaming, look fairly clean and well-maintained.  While it does have 
that peculiar bathroom smell, it doesn't reek, either.  The graffiti 
is minimal, though one particular bit catches the eye: "For good training, 
call the Hitokiri Battousai at the Kamiya Dojo."
~
