#13519
Welcome to `#K`*a`8ns`*a`#s``.~
Large lights surrond the entrance to the bar. People come from far and wide 
to relax and enjoy the atmosphere of this place. Different fragrances dance 
through the air, and make the place seem warm and inviting. Black lights line 
the walls and illuminate the beautifully carved stones that make up the outer 
edge of the bar. Full of faces and many other things, this place seems to 
shine out among all of the other sights in the city of neo-Toyko. There is a 
poster nailed to the far wall that attracts your attention.
